364
00:22:48,329 --> 00:22:49,669
- Brother Kai. 
 - Xiaoning.

365
00:22:49,669 --> 00:22:51,269
What did Director Xu want from you?

366
00:22:51,269 --> 00:22:53,670
Not me, he was looking for Director Gu.

367
00:22:53,670 --> 00:22:55,590
- Where's Director Gu? 
 - I don't know.

368
00:22:55,590 --> 00:22:58,449
He texted me this morning and told me I don't need to pick him up.

369
00:22:58,449 --> 00:23:01,410
He might be resting at home.

370
00:23:01,410 --> 00:23:03,369
I called him more than 10 times. He never picked up.

371
00:23:03,369 --> 00:23:06,830
- How about you go and check on him? 
 - Me?

372
00:23:06,830 --> 00:23:08,449
Definitely not me.

373
00:23:08,450 --> 00:23:10,630
You're his assistant.

374
00:23:11,930 --> 00:23:13,790
Sure, I'll go now.

375
00:23:13,790 --> 00:23:16,629
Xiaoning, get him some food on the way there.

376
00:23:16,629 --> 00:23:18,769
