377
00:23:18,769 --> 00:23:20,470
Sure!

378
00:23:36,470 --> 00:23:37,870
Boss.

379
00:23:37,870 --> 00:23:40,029
Did I not tell you to not come and pick me up today?

380
00:23:40,029 --> 00:23:42,389
Brother Kai said he called you a bunch of times and you never picked up.

381
00:23:42,389 --> 00:23:43,709
He wanted me to check whether you're home or not.

382
00:23:43,709 --> 00:23:47,030
He also said that your fridge needs to be stocked.

383
00:23:48,450 --> 00:23:50,690
You seem to have a lot of free time.

384
00:23:50,690 --> 00:23:53,470
Do you still remember that model from yesterday?

385
00:23:56,930 --> 00:23:58,769
