389
00:24:05,070 --> 00:24:06,830
Gu!

390
00:24:06,830 --> 00:24:10,050
Okay, go and do the check-in first.

391
00:24:15,550 --> 00:24:17,650
Come, Manlin.

392
00:24:20,650 --> 00:24:23,329
Is Uncle okay? Is he not happy?

393
00:24:24,430 --> 00:24:27,250
He's okay. He's always like that.

394
00:24:28,690 --> 00:24:32,930
I have no one else to talk to about this, except for you.

395
00:24:32,930 --> 00:24:35,270
Auntie, just say it. it's fine.

396
00:24:35,270 --> 00:24:38,289
Our Chuan has been living a lonely life these past years.

397
00:24:38,289 --> 00:24:39,729
He doesn't get along well with others.

398
00:24:39,730 --> 00:24:43,670
