401
00:24:50,670 --> 00:24:51,950
I understand.

402
00:24:51,950 --> 00:24:55,230
We'll spend more time with him.

403
00:24:55,230 --> 00:24:56,189
That would be great.

404
00:24:56,189 --> 00:24:59,690
