406
00:25:05,969 --> 00:25:07,709
A girl that he likes?

407
00:25:07,709 --> 00:25:09,410
Yes.

408
00:25:09,410 --> 00:25:12,930
He told us that she is his assistant.

409
00:25:12,930 --> 00:25:15,289
He's my child.

410
00:25:15,290 --> 00:25:16,970
I know him better than anyone.

411
00:25:16,970 --> 00:25:20,750
Even Chuan himself probably isn't aware of how much he likes her.

412
00:25:21,810 --> 00:25:25,590
