413
00:25:25,590 --> 00:25:28,510
Yes, that's the name.

414
00:25:28,510 --> 00:25:32,229
Right, you guys work in the same company. Are you close with her?

415
00:25:33,730 --> 00:25:35,890
We're okay.

416
00:25:37,830 --> 00:25:40,189
To be honest, we don't expect anything from him.

417
00:25:40,189 --> 00:25:42,109
