419
00:25:46,170 --> 00:25:49,829
I hope that Chengran and you, as friends, can take good care of them.

420
00:25:49,829 --> 00:25:53,249
Just pretend that you don't know anything, and let him do his thing.

421
00:25:53,249 --> 00:25:58,229
As for what will happen in the future and whether they can be together, it just depends on them.

422
00:26:01,890 --> 00:26:04,750
Manlin, is that okay?

423
00:26:06,450 --> 00:26:07,009
Of course.

424
00:26:07,010 --> 00:26:08,449
