501
00:30:38,630 --> 00:30:40,770
No, I like you.

502
00:30:40,770 --> 00:30:43,569
Thank you. I like myself too.

503
00:30:43,569 --> 00:30:45,409
What do you not like about me? Tell me! I can change.

504
00:30:45,409 --> 00:30:48,469
What do you like about me? I'll change.

505
00:30:48,469 --> 00:30:51,130
Everything.

506
00:30:51,130 --> 00:30:53,050
Nice.

507
00:30:54,090 --> 00:30:55,740
